title: [FSX/P3D] Aerosoft English Electric Lightning F3 X v1.0
description:
Aerosoft English Electric Lightning F3 X v1.0. Compatible with FSX SP2/Acceleration, P3D v1 and P3D v2. Crack and instructions are included.

I don't know why, but no one has bothered to share this one here at TPB although it has been more than a month since this aircraft was first released. I'm not interested in jets and airliners that much anymore, but I thought fellow pirates here might want this. Please seed this aircraft if you like it because I don't want to seed it forever.

Enjoy!
